doc.after: The Trident Regional Medical Center is the major hospital located in North Charleston There are several other hospitals located throughout the area serving city residents including the Medical University of South Carolina Ralph H Johnson VA Medical Center Bon Secours St Francis Xavier Hospital and Roper Hospital located in Charleston The East Cooper Regional Medical Center located in Mount Pleasant is another local hospital serving North Charleston residents
